Titolo: XIII (2020 video game)

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: XIII is a first-person shooter video game developed by PlayMagic Ltd. and published by Microids for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on November 10, 2020 and for Nintendo Switch in 2021. It is a remake of the 2003 video game of the same name.
XIII received negative reviews from critics and players. It was criticized for its changes to the art style, game design differences from the original and the game's technical and audio issues.